To make the code readable, introduce vring_need_unmap_buffer() to
replace do_unmap.

   use_dma_api premapped -> vring_need_unmap_buffer()
1. false       false        false
2. true        false        true
3. true        true         false

Signed-off-by: Xuan Zhuo <xuanzhuo@linux.alibaba.com>
Acked-by: Jason Wang <jasowang@redhat.com>
